          <h2>Welcomed to the <em>Lord's table</em></h2>
          <p>From the youngest children admitted to First Holy Communion, to those confirmed by the Bishop, we walk with each person as they take their next step in the life of faith — surrounded by the prayers of the whole community.</p>
